”Alexa, ask My Real Estate Advisor about buying a house”
”Alexa, ask My Real Estate Advisor how to sell a house”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my real estate advisor
Developer Terms of Use
des:
A home buyer or home seller often face unexpected requirements in their real estate transaction that could become unexpected costs. They can manage money better by learning what to expect!
 
My Real Estate Advisor guides you through high level keys steps and can send you the Home Buyer Guide or the Home Seller Guide filled with details to prepare you.
